@startuml
title American Latin Class - System Context
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAF7
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #242424
}
skinparam ArrowColor #9A8700

actor Visitante
actor Estudiante
actor Profesor
actor "Director de sede" as BranchDirector
actor "Director general" as GeneralDirector
actor Administrador

rectangle "American Latin Class Platform" as ALC {
  rectangle "Public academy experience\nprograms, branches, maps, enrollment" as Public
  rectangle "Academic management\naccounts, groups, classes, attendance, events" as Academic
  rectangle "Management control\nfinance, reports, analytics and audit" as Management
}

cloud "Google Identity Services" as GoogleIdentity
cloud "Google Maps" as GoogleMaps
cloud "Transactional email service" as Email
database "PostgreSQL / Amazon RDS" as Database

Visitante --> Public : explores and requests enrollment
Estudiante --> Academic : profile, events, payments, attendance, justifications
Profesor --> Academic : classes, roster, attendance, check-in/out
BranchDirector --> Academic : branch operation and follow-up
BranchDirector --> Management : branch reports
GeneralDirector --> Academic : academy-wide management
GeneralDirector --> Management : financial/attendance reports and analytics
Administrador --> Academic : accounts, roles and operational support
Administrador --> Management : audit and security oversight

Public --> GoogleMaps : branch maps and directions
Academic --> GoogleIdentity : optional login for existing account
Academic --> Email : access invitation and temporary credential
ALC --> Database : persistent transactional and analytical data

note bottom of ALC
The attendance system is the private operational platform
of the American Latin Class dance academy; the public landing
page promotes the academy, not the software itself.
end note
@enduml
